Package: veja-1960-cab-lv2
Architecture: arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, libsndfile1
Description: VeJa Marshall 1960 Cabinet LV2 plugin (pistomp fork)
 Marshall 1960A guitar cabinet convolver that loads IR .wav files from
 the bundle directory at runtime. Patched to support arbitrary JACK
 period sizes and to use bundle_path instead of a hardcoded /root/.lv2/
 prefix so the plugin works when installed anywhere.
